      "text": "5. Embedding Service\nPrecompute + cache keyed by content hash in LanceDB\nModel version stamping prevents mixed embedding spaces",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5. Embedding Service\nPrecompute + cache keyed by content hash in LanceDB\nModel version stamping prevents mixed embedding spaces",
