      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "11. Precompute vs On-the-Fly\nHybrid strategy: deterministic transforms precomputed\nCheap random augmentations stay live in the training loader",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "11. Precompute vs On-the-Fly\nHybrid strategy: deterministic transforms precomputed\nCheap random augmentations stay live in the training loader",
